               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝnä Māryām ba-Dabra Golgota, Prayer of Our Lady Mary
                     on Mount Golgotha on the 21st of Sane (fols. 1r-40v)
 II) Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt
                     “Teaching of Mysteries” (fols. 41r-54r)
 III) ʾAsmat-prayer against snake
                     bites (fols. 54v-55v)
 IV) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols.
                     56r-74v)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
