                        <condition key="deficient">The boards are re-used, might originate from a
                           different Ms.
 The sewing is damaged, partly missing.
 The board
                           attachments are crudely repaired with recent synthetic threads.
 Some
                           fols. are damaged by rodents and fire (s. fols. 1-12).
 Mould is
                           visible on <locus target="#70v">70v</locus> and 71r.
 A tear is
                           carefully amended on <locus target="#75">75</locus>.</condition>
