               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0178QMM">Märgaḥǝya Qǝddus Mikāʾel / QMM</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1820" notAfter="1850">ʿAsratä Māryām also wrote Mss
                        GMS-010, datable to 1841-52, DMA-009 and DMD-007. Perhaps this Ms. belongs
                        to one of his earlier productions.</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>The name of the original donors or owners has
                     been erased (2v, 40v, on 54r only a part of the name, Ṣǝyon, is readable), but appears still
                     readable in the supplication (addded later, but in the main hand?) on 74v: Habta Śǝllāse.</provenance></history>
